parameters: Gather the required materials to make accessories and more.
Gift your creations to the girls to increase their affection.
To save the declining elf village and the World Tree,
have sex with the elf girls and make babies！
There are no game overs or time limits,
so enjoy a carefree, slow impregnation life at your own pace.
By having sex with the girls, giving them gifts,
and interacting with them, your affection level will increase.
When certain conditions like affection level and number of births are met, your affection level will rise,
increasing conception rates or triggering new events.
Once you become intimate enough with a girl, you can even marry her,
so actively pursue them and raise your affection level.
The number of elves has decreased, and the World Tree has weakened.
Have babies with the girls to increase the population and restore the World Tree's vitality.
The conception rate during baby-making is influenced by the girl's affection level and menstrual cycle.
Become closer with the girls and aim for their fertile days to increase chances of conception.
As the World Tree recovers, crop yields will increase, and
various other benefits will arise, so keep making babies and having more children.
The number of elves has decreased, and the village is in decline.
You can develop the village by donating money.
Money can be earned by shipping crops grown in the fields,
or by selling items you've obtained, such as fish or ores.
As the village develops, more facilities will become available, houses can be expanded, and
new activities will unlock, so keep donating generously.
